==English==

===Noun===

'''waster'''

#One who, or that which, [[waste|wastes]]; one who [[squander|squanders]]; one who [[consume|consumes]] or [[expend|expends]] [[extravagant|extravagantly]]; a [[spendthrift]]; a [[prodigal]].
#An [[imperfection]] in the [[wick]] of a [[candle]], causing it to [[waste]]; -- called also a [[thief]].
#A kind of [[cudgel]]; also, a [[blunt]]-edged [[sword]] used as a [[foil]].

